claim.claim-text:
A steam generator (13), which is provided with the vibration suppression device of the heat transfer tube (100, 200, 300, 400, 500) according to any one of claims 1 to 12, comprising:
a body portion (61) that has a hollow airtight shape;
a heat transfer tube group (67) that is provided to form a reverse U-shape in the body portion (61) and is formed of a plurality of heat transfer tubes (66) in which first cooling water flows;
a tube plate (64) that is fixed to a lower portion in the body portion (61) and supports end portions of the plurality of heat transfer tubes (66);
an inlet side channel head (71) and an outlet side channel head (72) that are provided at a lower end portion of the body portion (61) and communicate with each end portion of the plurality of heat transfer tubes (66);
a water supply portion that supplies secondary cooling water into the body portion (61); and
a steam outlet (78) that is provided at an upper end portion of the body portion (61).
